3v9r54v1hj77dv7s3h19nv4ef1@google.com	3	STEAM Museum	\n\n\n\nJune 3rd Schedule\n9:00-9:40  3D, 3E\n10:15 -10:55 K4, K5\n11:45-12:25  1D, 1E\n12:50-1:30 4D, 4E\n1:35- 2:15  4C, 2D\n2:20-3:00 2C, 3C\n\n\nSTEAM Museum\nPortable Hands-On STEAM Museum\nTuesday, January 29th and Wednesday, January 30th 2019\n\nPerformer will arrive 2 hours prior to the performance time to load-in.\nSchool will provide one custodian to assist with loading and unloading.\nAn indoor 50' x 50' space (gym, multipurpose room) for the entire day. Performance area to be clear of clutter.\nSix adult volunteers to assist during the sessions all day.\n60 students per session with a maximum of six sessions. Sessions are 40 minutes in length with a five minute transition. (We have 12 sessions between the 2 days - will need a schedule)\nLunch and breaks required for three or more sessions.\nEight - 6' or 8' banquet tables to be set up the night before. Three electrical outlets.\n90 minutes for performer and school custodian to tear-down and load-out.\nA minimum of ten exhibits will be available on the day of the show.	2019-06-03 00:00:00+00	2019-06-04 00:00:00+00	f	Main Gym	CONFIRMED	d22a33df-1651-452f-8a5b-f0e99e6c02d1	BEGIN:VEVENT\r\nDTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20190603\r\nDTEND;VALUE=DATE:20190604\r\nDTSTAMP:20260315T192238Z\r\nORGANIZER;CN=min201.org_25p1q9uqg8a0ksdplsisigvgj4@group.calendar.google.co\r\n m:mailto:min201.org_25p1q9uqg8a0ksdplsisigvgj4@group.calendar.google.com\r\nUID:3v9r54v1hj77dv7s3h19nv4ef1@google.com\r\nATTENDEE;CUTYPE=INDIVIDUAL;ROLE=REQ-PARTICIPANT;PARTSTAT=NEEDS-ACTION;CN=al\r\n arson@min201.org;X-NUM-GUESTS=0:mailto:alarson@min201.org\r\nATTENDEE;CUTYPE=INDIVIDUAL;ROLE=REQ-PARTICIPANT;PARTSTAT=NEEDS-ACTION;CN=ME\r\n S_All;X-NUM-GUESTS=0:mailto:mes_all@min201.org\r\nATTENDEE;CUTYPE=INDIVIDUAL;ROLE=REQ-PARTICIPANT;PARTSTAT=NEEDS-ACTION;CN=dp\r\n laskett@min201.org;X-NUM-GUESTS=0:mailto:dplaskett@min201.org\r\nCREATED:20180612T162133Z\r\nDESCRIPTION:\\n\\n\\n\\nJune 3rd Schedule\\n9:00