6b7fk1iheri1pnki0u17q6su5a@google.com	3	Communicating to Bridge the Digital and Relationship Divide	Remote learning and school closures have highlighted inequities among students and families nationwide, especially in the area of internet and computer access. In this age of virtual and digital communications, how do we ensure all families are getting the information and access they deserve?\n\nJoin Dr. Susan Enfield, superintendent of Highline Public Schools, to learn how, in the face of the pandemic, Highline Public Schools are fulfilling their promise to know every student by name, strength and need. Dr. Enfield has dedicated her career to advocating for equity: Come be inspired and learn how you can leverage your communications to advocate for all students and put equity at the center of the conversation.	2021-04-23 17:30:00+00	2021-04-23 18:15:00+00	f	https://finalsite.zoom.us/j/93342050536	CONFIRMED	e849c968-c343-4e36-b218-3a8aefef1dc1	BEGIN:VEVENT\r\nDTSTART:20210423T173000Z\r\nDTEND:20210423T181500Z\r\nDTSTAMP:20260315T192238Z\r\nUID:6b7fk1iheri1pnki0u17q6su5a@google.com\r\nCREATED:20210423T124525Z\r\nDESCRIPTION:Remote learning and school closures have highlighted inequities\r\n  among students and families nationwide\\, especially in the area of interne\r\n t and computer access. In this age of virtual and digital communications\\, \r\n how do we ensure all families are getting the information and access they d\r\n eserve?\\n\\nJoin Dr. Susan Enfield\\, superintendent of Highline Public Schoo\r\n ls\\, to learn how\\, in the face of the pandemic\\, Highline Public Schools a\r\n re fulfilling their promise to know every student by name\\, strength and ne\r\n ed. Dr. Enfield has dedicated her career to advocating for equity: Come be \r\n inspired and learn how you can leverage your communications to advocate for\r\n  all students and put equity at the center of the conversation.\r\nLAST-MODIFIED:20210423T124525Z\r\nLOCATION:https://finalsite.zoom.us/j/9334205