2vtr3osmc6vee6s6ps3dpocq0e@google.com	3	Optoma Creative Touch Interactive Displays for Education	Join from a PC, Mac, iPad, iPhone or Android device:\n    Please click this URL to join. https://us02web.zoom.us/w/84841833016?tk=6UQM0rXNO9clb5b0aPA3lM-W6aAyYh9-MIqjx0CcYE4.DQMAAAATwPeiOBY2SXVYd1dBY1JteWJGd0hDWloyOTlBAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAA&uuid=WN_HD4uBqeiSP6zMQ4nwgaoYg\nDescription: Create. Connect. Teach\n\nOptoma’s Creative Touch 5-Series is more than just an interactive display, it delivers a truly intuitive and collaborative experience – giving teachers the tools to plan, create and deliver extraordinary lessons.  \n\nJoin this interactive session and see them in action, and how they can help enable collaboration and keep students engaged in your classrooms.  \n\nTEACHER LED TECHNOLOGY:\n\nFeatures designed for Teachers!\nWe will demonstrate how easy it is to present your lessons using our interactive features and functions\n\n•  Change tools at a touch with our customizable floating toolbar, with enhanced color palette and tool set\n•  Embedded browser - Access websites without leaving the whiteboard\n•  Never run out of space with our infinity canvas\n\nThese are just a few of the features and benefits included with Optoma interactive displays.\n\nOur technicians will be available to answer all of your questions.  Attendees will get a chance to win a $100 gift card!\n\nRegister below.\n\nOr One tap mobile:\n    +13092053325,,84841833016# US\n    +13126266799,,84841833016# US (Chicago)\n\nOr join by phone:\n    Dial(for higher quality, dial a number based on your current location):\n        US: +1 309 205 3325  or +1 312 626 6799  or +1 301 715 8592  or +1 305 224 1968  or +1 646 558 8656  or +1 646 931 3860  or +1 507 473 4847  or +1 564 217 2000  or +1 669 444 9171  or +1 669 900 9128  or +1 689 278 1000  or +1 719 359 4580  or +1 253 205 0468  or +1 253 215 8782  or +1 346 248 7799  or +1 360 209 5623  or +1 386 347 5053 \n    Webinar ID: 848 4183 3016\