56e68datdnbjjhoh3e1ubjhsu8@google.com	3	PTO Halloween Trunk or Treat/Dance Party	\n\n\nGrade level aides and all available staff not overseeing children,  please assist by standing at the south door and north door to oversee that no one enters those doors but the children and staff.  If it rains and the parade is moved indoors, please assist at the north end blocking off the main hallway as in the past years.  \n\nIndoor Parade\nRain Day Plan- Rain plan will be to simply parade around gym and back to classrooms.  PTO will come around with the trunk or treat-treats for children to your classrooms.  This will keep the line moving at a fast pace. We will welcome parents to view parade from the bleachers.  We will line  up and parade through gym as follows:\nGrade 3\nGrade 4\nGrade 1\nGrade 2\nKindergarten\n\n\nOutdoor Parade 9:15 Trunk or Treat parade\nPlease have all children ready in lines to proceed outdoors by 9:10AM.  \nTrunk or Treat Parade Line up starting at 9:00/9:05 but the parade will begin promptly at 9:15: \n\n\nGrade 4-Grade 4 teachers, please lead us out promptly at 9:15.  \nGrade 3-Please bring students down to line up behind grade 4 by 9:10\nGrade 1-Please line up behind grade 3 by 9:10\nGrade 2-Please have children line up behind grade 1 by 9:10\nKindergarten-Please line up in the west wing read to jump into line behind grade 1.  \n\n\nMonster Mash Dance Party in the gym/ Medical exclusion students will play Halloween Bingo  in the main gym\n(No Fine Arts-- teachers may take prep time during Dance Party, Fine Arts teachers to help supervise in gym)\n\n9:50-10:20-- Fourth\n10:25-10:55- Kindergarten\n11:00-11:30-- Third\n11:35-12:05-- First/Admin./PTO supervision/Fine Arts-Lunch\n12:10-12:40-- Second\n\nJoin with Google Meet: https://meet.google.com/yzb-mvdd-gek\nOr dial: (US) +1 575-616-5007 PIN: 657542171#\n\nLearn more about Meet at: https://support.google.com/a/users/answer/9282720	2019-10-31 00:00:00+00	2019-11-01 00:00:00+00	f	\N	CONFIRMED	1fcce07