55aroul2id4r3kddd69pa9r16l@google.com	3	PTO Laser Safari Assembly	Laser Safari\nPerformances at 1-1:45pm   K-2\n 2-2:45pm  Grades 3 and 4\n\n***There will be no afternoon PE. Please plan on splitting the time so that you get your 20 minute plan time.  The rest of the time you will report to the gym to supervise the students.  Aides should report to the gym to assist with supervision.  \n\n\n\n****************************************************************************************************\nMinimum power requirement is two 15-amp 120-volt lines from a standard source.\nClient will provide Vendor access to the location a minimum of 1.00 hours prior to the scheduled start time and 0.5 hours following the conclusion of the event.\nARRIVAL AND SETUP: It takes about an hour for us to set up and we bring absolutely everything we need.  Please be sure there is a good place for us to park and unload as we have a lot of equipment to bring into the school.  This video clip shows how we set up and how much space we need: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ruWD4fY0-rs.  We are able to modify the set up to fit just about any room, but this is our ideal layout. \n\nThe darker the room the better the program, so anything that you can do to darken the room is worth it.	2019-05-16 00:00:00+00	2019-05-17 00:00:00+00	f	Main Gym	CONFIRMED	9fd47c9a-0a98-42c7-ba7b-ffc31cc0bdeb	BEGIN:VEVENT\r\nDTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20190516\r\nDTEND;VALUE=DATE:20190517\r\nDTSTAMP:20260315T192238Z\r\nORGANIZER;CN=min201.org_25p1q9uqg8a0ksdplsisigvgj4@group.calendar.google.co\r\n m:mailto:min201.org_25p1q9uqg8a0ksdplsisigvgj4@group.calendar.google.com\r\nUID:55aroul2id4r3kddd69pa9r16l@google.com\r\nATTENDEE;CUTYPE=INDIVIDUAL;ROLE=REQ-PARTICIPANT;PARTSTAT=NEEDS-ACTION;CN=ME\r\n S_All;X-NUM-GUESTS=0:mailto:mes_all@min201.org\r\nATTENDEE;CUTYPE=INDIVIDUAL;ROLE=REQ-PARTICIPANT;PARTSTAT=NEEDS-ACTION;CN=dp\r\n laskett@min201.org;X-NUM-GUESTS=0:mailto:dplaskett@min201.org\r\nATTENDEE;CUTYPE=INDIVIDUAL;ROLE=REQ-PARTICIP