22	McKerrow Dream Dashboard notes	{"type": "doc", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "Meeting on March 13th", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "Discussion with Mac about data warehouse dreams. What are the big areas we are lacking from your lens?  We can meet in Mac's office or tech office table.", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 1, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "What are we lacking?", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}}]}	f	7	2026-03-12 12:31:14.390379	2026-03-12 12:33:55.913219
